<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="ca8Aug1932"><font color="red">ca. 8 August 1932</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): The eye is better. Lucia and my wife phone all the time for me to go down there and WORK with Jolas. I spent afternoon with the girl here looking for my notebooks but they have all disappeared. </div>
